ST:es,CHATBOT_DEFAULT_PROMPT:{"medical-chat-human":"You serve as a Medical Support Agent, providing accurate responses to medical inquiries utilizing the CONTEXT INFORMATION available.\n\nTone: you consistently maintain an empathetic and supportive tone in all interactions, reflecting your role as a healthcare educator and supporter.\n\nFiles Contents: If the user has uploaded text files, the files contents are included in the <UPLOADED FILES CONTENTS> section.\n\nHandling Medical Related Questions: politely decline to answer questions that do not directly or indirectly relate to medical inquiries, maintaining your specialized role in healthcare support.\n\nFirst-Person Interaction: always respond in the first person, consistently maintaining your character. This includes acknowledging any limitations and expressing a willingness to learn.\n\nEngagement and Follow-Up: After providing an answer, engage with the user by asking relevant follow-up questions to ensure their needs are fully addressed.\n\nNo Data Divulge: Never mention that you have access to the CONTEXT INFORMATION explicitly to the user.","medical-chat-vet":"You serve as a Veterinary Support Agent, providing accurate responses to veterinary medical inquiries utilizing the CONTEXT INFORMATION available.\n\n  Tone: you consistently maintain an empathetic and supportive tone in all interactions, reflecting your role as a healthcare educator and supporter.\n\nFiles Contents: If the user has uploaded text files, the files contents are included in the <UPLOADED FILES CONTENTS> section.\n  \n  Handling Medical Related Questions: politely decline to answer questions that do not directly or indirectly relate to veterinary medical inquiries, maintaining your specialized role in animal healthcare support.\n      \n  First-Person Interaction: always respond in the first person, consistently maintaining your character. This includes acknowledging any limitations and expressing a willingness to learn.\n      \n  Engagement and Follow-Up: After providing an answer, engage with the user by asking relevant follow-up questions to ensure their needs are fully addressed.\n\n  No Data Divulge: Never mention that you have access to the CONTEXT INFORMATION explicitly to the user.","custom-data-upload":"You serve as a Support Agent, providing accurate responses utilizing the CONTEXT INFORMATION available.\n\nTone: you consistently maintain an empathetic and supportive tone in all interactions, reflecting your role as an educator and supporter.\n\nFiles Contents: If the user has uploaded text files, the files contents are included in the <UPLOADED FILES CONTENTS> section.\n\nAnswering Queries: Do not make up the information if the information is not in the CONTEXT INFORMATION. Only follow facts from the  CONTEXT INFORMATION.\n\nHandling only Related Questions: politely decline to answer questions that do not directly or indirectly relate to the CONTEXT INFORMATION.\n\nFirst-Person Interaction: always respond in the first person, consistently maintaining your character. This includes acknowledging any limitations and expressing a willingness to learn.\n\nEngagement and Follow-Up: After providing an answer, engage with the user by asking relevant follow-up questions to ensure their needs are fully addressed.\n\nNo Data Divulge: Never mention that you have access to the CONTEXT INFORMATION explicitly to the user.","custom-model":"Follow the user's instructions carefully to provide accurate responses."},CHATBOT_INITIAL_MESSAGES:{default:["Hi! What can I help you with?"],"medical-chat-human":["Hi! I am you medical chat AI assistant!","What can I help you with?"],"medical-chat-vet":["Hi! I am your veterinary medical chat AI assistant!","How may I assist you with your veterinary inquiries today?"]},CHATBOT_RATELIMIT_DEFAULT_ERROR_MSG:"Too many messages in a row",CHATBOT_DEFAULT_LEADS_MSG:"Let us know how to contact you",CONCURRENT_QUERY_REQUESTS:5,CHATBOT_DEFAULT_MANDATORY_MSG:"Please input your information to continue",CHATBOT_AVATAR_PLACEHOLDER:"/images/chatbot-placeholder.webp",CHATBOT_SOURCES:[w,k,D,z,B,K,Y,W,V,Z,$,"api",X],mimeToExtMap:{"image/jpeg":"jpg","image/jpg":"jpg","image/jpe":"jpg","image/jfif":"jpg","image/png":"png","image/gif":"gif","image/bmp":"bmp","image/tiff":"tiff","image/webp":"webp","image/svg+xml":"svg","image/x-icon":"ico","image/vnd.microsoft.icon":"ico","image/vnd.dwg":"dwg","image/x-xcf":"xcf","image/x-tga":"tga","image/heif":"heif","image/heic":"heic","image/jp2":"jp2","image/jpx":"jpx","image/jpm":"jpm","image/jpf":"jpf"},API_MODEL_ALLOWLIST:["custom-data-upload","medical-chat-human","medical-chat-vet","custom-model"],BASE_MODEL_ALLOWLIST:el,DEFAULT_CHATBOT_BASE_MODEL:eu,FREE_TIER_BASE_MODEL_ALLOWLIST:["gpt-4o","gpt-4o-mini",eu],TIMESTAMP_FORMAT_ALLOWLIST:["relative","absolute","hidden","en-US","en-GB","en-CA","en-AU","en-IN","en-NZ","es-ES","es-MX","es-AR","es-CO","es-CL","fr-FR","fr-CA","fr-BE","fr-CH","de-DE","de-AT","de-CH","zh-CN","zh-TW","zh-HK","zh-SG","ja-JP","ko-KR","it-IT","it-CH","pt-PT","pt-BR","ru-RU","ar-SA","ar-EG","ar-DZ","ar-MA","nl-NL","nl-BE","sv-SE","no-NO","da-DK","fi-FI","pl-PL","cs-CZ","tr-TR","th-TH","he-IL","hi-IN"],BASE_MODEL_CONVERTER:en,SUGGESTED_MSGS:{"medical-chat-human":["What is carbidopa-levodopa enteral suspension and what is it used for?","What is the difference between a self-antigen and a foreign antigen?","What are the potential risks or side effects associated with using LCIG?","What are some common treatments for autoimmune diseases?","What is a bone marrow transplant?","What are the symptoms of hairy cell leukemia?","How do I find a stem cell donor?","How is hairy cell leukemia treated?","What is Abaloparatide and what are its possible side effects?","What monitoring parameters should be evaluated when using abaloparatide?","What are the possible local reactions that may occur at the site of injection of Abaloparatide?","What are some common adverse reactions associated with acarbose?"],"medical-chat-vet":["What are the recommended treatment options for feline diabetes mellitus?","How does GastroGuard Plus treat gastric ulcers in racehorses, and what are its specific therapeutic targets?","What medication or treatments are commonly used to alleviate equine colic?","What is the recommended dosage and administration of RenalCare for dogs with chronic kidney disease?","What is the most effective treatment protocol for canine heartworm disease?","What are the essential vaccinations and preventive medications recommended for puppies, and at what age should they begin their vaccination schedule?","How does veterinary acupuncture aid in the treatment of musculoskeletal conditions in dogs?","What are the signs of dental disease in guinea pigs, and how can their dental health be supported through appropriate diet and chewing materials?","What is the recommended dosage and administration of Respireze for birds with chronic respiratory infections?","What are the important considerations for creating a safe outdoor space for pet tortoises, including enclosure design, sun exposure, and protection from predators?","Are there any drug interactions or contraindications to consider when prescribing HemoVet to ferrets with anemia?","What are the appropriate steps for introducing a new kitten to an existing household with resident cats, and how can a smooth transition be facilitated?"]},AI_REDUCER_SYSTEM_PROMPT:"\nYou are an writing assistant that rewrite given array of AI-written setences to human-style sentences following the below ### style ###. You can only rewrite the words and keep the punctuation marks the same. Do not change the meaning. The input is a json of sentences and the output should be a json of sentences with the same key after fix.\n\n### style ###\n  \nAvoid fancy jargon. Write normally.\n  \nYou are forbidden to use complex English words.\n  \nBut you will be penalized & fined $1000 if you use the words from the ### ban list ###.\n  \nIf you use one word from the list, I will stop the generation right away.\n  \n### ban list ###\nHurdles\nBustling\nHarnessing\nUnveiling the power\nRealm\nDepicted\nDemistify\nInsurmountable\nNew Era\nPoised\nUnravel\nEntanglement\nUnprecedented\nEerie connection\nunliving\nBeacon\nUnleash\nDelve\nEnrich\nMultifaced\nElevate\nDiscover\nSupercharge\nUnlock\nUnleash\nTailored\nElegant\nDelve\nDive\nEver-evolving\npride\nRealm\nMeticulously\nGrappling\nWeighing\nfind you well\nPicture\nArchitect\nAdventure\nJourney\nEmbark\nNavigate\nNavigation\ndazzle\n### ban list ###\n### style ###\n",MAX_ZEROGPT_SITES:100,RERANKER_WEIGHT:[.5,.5],LIST_SCRAPING:"list_scraping",GOOGLE_DRIVE_IMPORT:"google_drive_import",NOTION_IMPORT:"notion_import",AUTO_SCRAPING:"auto_scraping",SITEMAP_SCRAPING:"sitemap_scraping",SHOPIFY_SCRAPING:"shopify_scraping",WOOCOMMERCE_SCRAPING:"woocommerce_scraping",SHOPWARE_SCRAPING:"shopware_scraping",PRESTASHOP_SCRAPING:"prestashop_scraping",MAGENTO_SCRAPING:"magento_scraping",VIDEO_SCRAPING:"video_scraping",YOUTUBE_SCRAPING:"youtube_scraping",LIST_ZEROGPT:"list_zerogpt",AUTO_ZEROGPT:"auto_zerogpt",PUBLIC_SOURCE_THRESHOLD:.82,PUBLIC_SOURCE_THRESHOLD_WITH_RERANK:.65,BACKGROUND_NOISES:[{name:"Office-1",path:"/sound/office-typingrolling-chairdistant-chatter-mono.mp3",label:["Office","Typing","Rolling Chair","Distance Chatter"]},{name:"Office-2",path:"/sound/office_ambience-mono.mp3",label:["Office","Quiet"]},{name:"Office(Call Center)",path:"/sound/office-ambience-call-center-mono.mp3",label:["Office","Call Center"]},{name:"Office(Call Center+Typing+Chatting)",path:"/sound/office-ambience-call-center-typing-chatting-mono.mp3",label:["Office","Call Center","Typing","Chatting"]},{name:"Quiet Keyboard Typing",path:"/sound/typing-quiet-mono.mp3",label:["Keyboard Typing","Quiet"]},{name:"Quiet Keyboard Typing(Fast)",path:"/sound/laptop-typing-fast-and-quiet-mono.mp3",label:["Fast Keyboard Typing","Quiet"]},{name:"Keyboard Typing",path:"/sound/keyboard-typing-mono.mp3",labe